modules.description: Handles request routing, response generation, and connection management for Gemini protocol servers. Processes text and binary data streams, and manages HTTP-like status codes and headers. Used to create real-time chat servers, static file hosts, and API endpoints compliant with Gemini standards.

Provides functions to serve static files and generate directory listings, using a specified MIME type or defaulting to none. Operates on file system paths, request addresses, and custom handlers for HTTP responses. Handles file retrieval, directory validation, and conditional listing of files with options for index files and hidden file visibility.
